OL,3,CLeicester City helicopter crash which
OL,4,Ckilled five people ruled accidental
OL,6,FSenior coroner Catherine Mason
OL,7,Finstructed the jury before they began
OL,8,Ftheir deliberations that only an
OL,9,Faccidental conclusion could be reached.
OL,11,FThe jury's conclusion, which was read
OL,12,Fto the hearing by the foreperson,
OL,13,Fsaid: "The helicopter had all
OL,14,Fairworthiness and maintenance
OL,15,Fcertificates.
OL,17,F"It was found that the pilot, Eric
OL,18,FSwaffer, took all available and
OL,19,Fappropriate options to try to regain
OL,20,Fcontrol of the helicopter."
