OL,4,Ckilled five people ruled accidental
OL,6,FMr Srivaddhanaprabha's family said the
OL,7,Fhelicopter a "death trap" and the
OL,8,Fcrash was an "accident waiting to
OL,9,Fhappen".
OL,11,FThey've alleged that the helicopter
OL,12,Fmanufacturer Leonardo S.p.A. is liable
OL,13,Ffor his death and launched a #2.15
OL,14,Fbillion legal claim before the inquest
OL,15,Fbegan.
OL,17,FThe family's lawyer, Philip Shepherd
OL,18,FKC, read a statement after the inquest
OL,19,Fsaying:
OL,26,@pD@NOUqD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/17
