OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F371A1738159011
OL,3,CLeicester City helicopter crash which
OL,4,Ckilled five people ruled accidental
OL,6,F"Whilst it was no part of the inquest
OL,7,Fprocess to apportion blame, the
OL,8,Fevidence heard during this inquest
OL,9,Ftold the story of basic engineering
OL,10,Ffailures by Leonardo.
OL,12,F"The inquest heard evidence that the
OL,13,Fdesign was such that it was just a
OL,14,Fmatter of time before something
OL,15,Fcatastrophic occurred, it was an
OL,16,Faccident waiting to happen.
OL,18,F"They were innocent victims of a
OL,19,Ftragic accident that never needed to
OL,20,Fhappen.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/17
