OL,3,CLeicester City helicopter crash which
OL,4,Ckilled five people ruled accidental
OL,6,F"During the two-and-a-half-week
OL,7,Finquest, the jury heard that the
OL,8,Fhelicopter crashed even though it was
OL,9,Fstill new, even though it was properly
OL,10,Fmaintained, and even though it met the
OL,11,Fminimum certification standards, and
OL,12,Feven though there was no pilot error
OL,13,Fwhatsoever.
OL,15,F"The family of Khun Vichai continues
OL,16,Fto search for justice and
OL,17,Faccountability."
OL,19,FLeonardo S.p.A. responded to these
OL,20,Fclaims saying:
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/17
