OL,3,CLeicester City helicopter crash which
OL,4,Ckilled five people ruled accidental
OL,6,F"Leonardo agrees with the inquest
OL,7,Fjury's conclusion that this crash was
OL,8,Fa tragic accident.
OL,10,F"As the jury recorded, the helicopter
OL,11,Fhad all the relevant airworthiness
OL,12,Fcertificates.
OL,14,F"This is entirely consistent with the
OL,15,Fevidence provided to the inquest, that
OL,16,Fthe helicopter was designed and
OL,17,Fproduced in accordance with all
OL,18,Fregulatory requirements, meeting the
OL,19,Faccepted industry standard for safety.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
