OL,6,F"Leonardo reiterates its deepest
OL,7,Fsympathies and condolences for those
OL,8,Fwho lost their lives in the accident,
OL,9,Fall of them clearly loved by their
OL,10,Ffamilies, friends and communities.
OL,12,F"Their deaths were an unquestionable
OL,13,Ftragedy."
OL,15,FMs Mason said: "Five innocent lives
OL,16,Fwere cruelly lost on October 27 2018,
OL,17,Flives that were cut too short.
OL,26,@uD@IO]wD@POU
