OL,6,F"This huge loss will be borne by the
OL,7,Ffamilies for the rest of their lives,
OL,8,Fa loss that is also felt by the
OL,9,Fcommunity of Leicester.
OL,11,F"It has been a long journey. Just over
OL,12,Fsix years for you, the families, to
OL,13,Fget the answers you wanted as to how
OL,14,Fyour loved ones came by their deaths.
OL,16,F"I hope you feel through these
OL,17,Finquests that you now have a voice."
OL,19,FMs Mason also praised the emergency
OL,20,Fservice workers who responded to the
OL,21,Fcrash:
