OL,6,FA report which was published by the
OL,7,FAir Accident Investigation Branch
OL,8,Flooking into the incident in 2023,
OL,9,Fdescribed it as a "tragic accident".
OL,11,FIt revealed the seizure of the tail
OL,12,Frotor duplex bearing initiated a
OL,13,Fsequence of failures. It culminated in
OL,14,Fthe unrecoverable loss of control.
OL,16,FThe 11 jurors had to answer four
OL,17,Fquestions: who was each deceased
OL,18,Fperson, when did they die, where did
OL,19,Fthey die, and how did they come by
OL,20,Ftheir death.
