OL,4,Ckilled five people ruled accidental
OL,6,FThe helicopter crashed onto its left
OL,7,Fhand side on a 0.5m concrete step
OL,8,Fcreating a "substantial" fuel leak
OL,9,Fwhich ignited the rear of the
OL,10,Fhelicopter within a minute of the
OL,11,Fimpact before flames "rapidly"
OL,12,Fconsumed the helicopter, the jury had
OL,13,Fheard.
OL,15,FJurors were told four of the five
OL,16,Fpeople killed in the crash died
OL,17,Fbecause of smoke inhalation after the
OL,18,Ffire started, while Ms Lechowicz
OL,19,F"likely died at the point of impact"
OL,20,Ffrom traumatic injuries to her head
OL,21,Fand chest.
