OL,7,Falso told the inquest there was no
OL,8,Fevidence to suggest the pilot was
OL,9,Fmedically incapacitated at the time of
OL,10,Fthe crash.
OL,12,FThe court heard Mr Swaffer's actions
OL,13,Freduced the rate of the helicopter's
OL,14,Fspin while he tried to "cushion" its
OL,15,Fimpact in disorientating conditions,
OL,16,Fbut "a crash landing was inevitable".
